### Test Floor-Wise Notification API

### 1. Get Floor Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/notification/floors
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 2. Send Notification to Specific Floors
POST http://localhost:3000/notification/send-to-floors
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "floors": [1, 2],
  "title": "Floor Meeting Announcement",
  "message": "All students on floors 1 and 2, please gather in the common area at 6 PM today for an important announcement."
}

### 3. Send to Single Floor
POST http://localhost:3000/notification/send-to-floors
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "floors": [3],
  "title": "Floor 3 Maintenance Notice",
  "message": "Water supply will be temporarily shut off on floor 3 tomorrow from 10 AM to 2 PM for maintenance work."
}

### 4. Test with Image URL
POST http://localhost:3000/notification/send-to-floors
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "floors": [1, 2, 3],
  "title": "Event Invitation",
  "message": "Join us for the hostel cultural night this Saturday at 7 PM!",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/event-poster.jpg"
}
